<plot>From a troubadour's guitar spins the tale of Javier, a recent Ecuadorian immigrant, who longs for Olivia, the woman he serves from behind the deli counter every day. Shyly flirtatious Olivia tells him in stumbling Spanish that they will finally meet for a romantic rendezvous "cuando la luna esta llena" - when the moon is full.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?653551</url></doc>
